  <brief_title>Influence of Nutrition on Nasal and Bronchial Affliction in Patients With Allergy on Grass-Pollen</brief_title>
  <official_title>Influence of Nutrition on Nasal and Bronchial Affliction in Patients With Allergy on Grass-Pollen After Low-Dosed Specific Bronchial Provocation</official_title>
