  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  age &gt;12 and &lt;45 years

          -  informed consent

          -  Known allergy on grass-pollen

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  age &lt;12 and &gt;45 years

          -  Clinical asthma requiring regular inhalation

          -  vital capacity &gt;80%

          -  FEV1 &lt; 75%

          -  Chronic disease

          -  pregnancy

          -  Inhalative or systemic steroid use

          -  substance abuse

          -  incapability of understanding the study's purpose and performance
      </textblock>
